{"tid":1465871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔分化] 希望大家冷靜，諗下機場運動既原意","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:32.000Z","uid":305017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c1f0798fbc0092d5082bb23ef965ee8b1aaec8d","tid":1465871,"uid":305017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:23.000Z","msg":"希望機場既手足諗一諗<br />\n我地原本搞機場運動係想迫爆機場<br />\n令機場停止運作，比到壓力政府<br />\n但係今晚既情況已經偏離左<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家要保持冷靜，獨立思考!!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，重溫下梁天琦既信:<br />\n<br />\n當然，真正的公義還未來臨，你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。<br />\n<br />\n如是者，假如我們希望社會能夠寬容地看待被論定為「暴動」的「暴徒」，理解這些無聲者的訴求，接納這些無權者的諫言，我想，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？</span></span>"},{"pid":"81e4c4d73398ff50bf00da307f6a00a1fb269f6d","tid":1465871,"uid":39090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"梁天琦：懇請不要被仇恨支配自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請各位機場手足唔好激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你地啦 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好衝動啊 求下你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d458d3bb3fbd4e93d600a93a5cd3085c3e1bcdb1","tid":1465871,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:28:01.000Z","msg":"唔反對大家做任何事，但一定基於理性，有理有據"},{"pid":"93afb8eb72a50ddb5351c122c33238ede4eaee64","tid":1465871,"uid":47955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"認同，不如大家冷靜左先，唔好衝住，場運動唔會兩三個月就完，諗下點再做。"},{"pid":"655a0b48f18a0f7ee0eaf9be35551c42213e3410","tid":1465871,"uid":305017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"求下大家冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重新思考下一步點做<br />\n唔係一味死衝<br />\n機場唔係咁玩架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 